reviewText: I just ordered this set.  The Blanks are the best in the aerobic fitness world.  I own four of their DVD's and workout to them 4 - 5 times a week. Their workouts are as fun, and as challenging as you want to make them.  Their enthusiasm for exercise is infectious.  The dance routines vary in difficulty, but are always a joy to do.  Billy and Sharon Catherine Blanks are the best teachers of dance aerobics in this America.  I love their workout and look forward to new DVD's  If you wan't to be fit and have fun try the DIO workouts.  I love them.
